              <p class="text-xs text-muted uppercase font-semibold mb-1">150 kWp × 4.5 Peak Sun Hours</p>
              <p class="font-anton text-4xl text-secondary">675 kWh</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-muted">per day (India/Africa average)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-muted/10 pb-2">
