            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-muted mt-3">Varies by village size, terrain, inter-household distance and backup requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-muted-foreground/5 border border-muted/20 rounded-2xl p-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-foreground mb-3">Scalable BESS — Add Capacity</h3>
